    To view or download California Career Planning Guide, you will need to
   have a copy of the Adobe Acrobat Reader installed on your computer.
   With the Adobe Acrobat Reader, you can either read the file on screen
   or download it to your computer to save or to print later.

     Which happens depends on how you have configured your browser.
   Generally, browsers such as Netscape Navigator and Internet Explorer
   allow you to save the file to disk or to use the Acrobat Reader plug-in
   to view the file.

   If you do not have Adobe Acrobat Reader, you can download a free copy
   for your computer from:

            http://www.adobe.com/prodindex/acrobat/readstep.html

   If you are ready to download the California Career Planning Guide,
   please click below:


